<p><strong>12.15-12.45</strong> <a href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/4042">Tools in use</a></p>
<p><strong>12.45-1.30</strong> Lunch</p>
<p><strong>1.30-2.00</strong> <a href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3422">Course map</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/4616"> video clip of activity</a></p>
