<p>9.30 &ndash; 9.45&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Arrival: Tea and Coffee </strong></p>
<p>9.45 &ndash; 9.55&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Welcome and Introductions </strong></p>
