<p>&nbsp;10.10.11.30&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Activity 1: Finding and sharing   resources and experiences on teaching and learning </strong></p>
<p>Participants will be split into groups. You will   discuss and also work through four of the five clouds on the following   topics:</p>
<p>Participants will be split into groups. You will   discuss and also work through four of the five clouds on the following   topics:</p>
<ul>
