<li>Clouds 4:   How might web 2.0 tools (such as Cloudworks) be used to support the design of   learning activities or OERs (20 mins</li>
<li>Cloud 5: Set   up a cloud on your own topic. Suggested topics you might like to consider   include: 
<ul>
