<li>What 3 words would you use to describe Cloudworks?</li>
<li>What 3 words would you use to describe CompendiumLD?</li>
<li>What action points have you identified as a result of this workshop?</li>
<li>What did you like about the format of the workshop?</li>
<li>What didn't you like or could be improved?</li>
</ul>]]></description>
          <pubDate>Fri, 06 Nov 2009 14:45:49 +0000</pubDate>
