              <title>Activity: 40 mins: Design review</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2599</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2599</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<h3>Click on image to enlarge</h3>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/44251404@N06/4074978676/"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3500/4074978676_22f23ac063_o.jpg" alt="Design review" hspace="25" width="300" height="300" align="right" /></a></p>
<p>In this activity evaluation/ reflection tools will be used to review teams' designs:</p>
<ul>
<li>Pedagogy profile</li>
<li>Course dimensions</li>
<li>How to ruin a course checklist</li>
</ul>
<p>Each tool looks at a different aspect of your design, and each has strengths and limitations. It is intended that they should work effectively together.</p>
<p>1. Use the 3 tools to review your design (no more than 10 mins per tool)</p>
<p>2. Make a list of the changes you will make as a consequence of the review</p>
<p>3. Amend the design, save it to your pen drive and add to Slideshare</p>
<p>4. Update your&nbsp; Cloud with progress update and images as appropriate</p>]]></description>
